# Cloudflare Pages routing rules.
# IMPORTANT: This file is OVERWRITTEN at build time by scripts/generate-robots.ts,
# which emits the canonical _redirects into /dist with draft → 410 rules.
# This /public/_redirects is only a safety net for non-standard builds.

# 0) Canonical host — force www → non-www (301). Consolidates ranking signal
#    onto https://gptbot.uz (audit flagged both hosts serving 200).
https://www.gptbot.uz/*  https://gptbot.uz/:splat  301

# 1) Admin SPA shell — React Router handles sub-routes client-side.
/admin-tools/*  /index.html  200

# 1a) Unprefixed blog URLs — 301 to the Russian locale so legacy/external
#     links and AI-generated citations without a language prefix don't 404.
/blog/*  /ru/blog/:splat  301

# 2) NO wildcard `/*` fallback by design. Unknown URLs must return 404 so they
#    don't get indexed as soft-duplicates of the homepage. Real money/blog
#    pages are served from their prerendered /dist/<path>/index.html files.
